  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Retail Sales Executive",
  "description": "<h3> Job Description</h3><p>We are looking for a friendly, responsible, and motivated <strong>Retail Sales Executive</strong> to join our ladies fashion retail team. You will be responsible for providing excellent customer service, supporting daily store operations, and driving sales performance.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Welcome and assist customers with product selection and styling advice</p></li><li><p>Promote store products and support sales targets</p></li><li><p>Operate POS system and handle cashless transactions</p></li><li><p>Manage stock replenishment and basic inventory checks</p></li><li><p>Maintain store cleanliness and visual merchandising standards</p></li><li><p>Support promotional activities and store events</p></li><li><p>Assist with folding, steaming, tagging, and organizing merchandise</p></li><li><p>Provide good customer service and build customer relationships</p></li></ul><h3>✅ Job Requirements (Female)</h3><ul><li><p>No prior experience required (training provided)</p></li><li><p>Interest in fashion retail and customer service</p></li><li><p>Able to communicate in basic English & Burmese.</p></li><li><p>Positive attitude and willingness to learn</p></li><li><p>Responsible and able to work independently after training</p></li><li><p>Able to commit to shift work, including weekends and public holidays<br /></p><p>* Only Singaporean, PR and LTVP</p></li></ul><h3>🕒 Working Hours</h3><ul><li><p>6 days per week <br /></p></li></ul><h3>💰 Salary & Benefits</h3><ul><li><p>Basic Salary + Fixed Allowance</p></li><li><p>Overtime Pay (according to MOM guidelines)</p></li><li><p>Performance Incentives (if applicable)</p></li><li><p>Staff Discount on store products</p></li></ul>",
